name: H2H Czech Series 2 (H2HCZEK2.WAD)
description: This is another pwad that I made for deathmatches on H2H in San Diego (619-426-0073). As you can see, it is not a deathmatch specific wad because the original idea was to design something similair to Id's shareware episode. This level is suitable also for single and co-op.
